# Force LF line endings for files that get executed inside Linux containers.
# Without this, Windows users who clone or extract the project can end up with
# CRLF in YAML / shell / Dockerfile content, which breaks Tesseract scripts,
# Temporal's Go YAML parser, and various Linux-only tooling.
*.yaml      text eol=lf
*.yml       text eol=lf
*.sh        text eol=lf
Dockerfile  text eol=lf
Dockerfile.* text eol=lf
*.conf      text eol=lf
